body_html: Yesterday I downloaded Tensorflow without a hitch as per the single line "pip install --upgrade tensorflow" instructions. Now I'm getting the exact same error.... and the distribution already includes that file you mention. The problem is: how is the ".h" file generated from this ".proto" file... if indeed that is what happens? Given that neither me nor the OP want any TPU support, how can we switch this off in the build? (my build has 240 successful projects, 2 failed projects, and the failures start with this error, then continue with roughly 570 LNK2005 errors from redefined functions)
